process_log:
Canvas: Light (Digital) (3840x2160). Base: #001133 (Deep Void Blue).
Composition: Guided by Rule of Thirds.
  [1] Structural Sketch: Drafting the skeleton of 'The True Form of Elysia' using Rule of Thirds.
  [2] Underpainting: Washing the canvas with #001133 (Deep Void Blue) to set the mood of Awe.
  [3] Form Integration: Sculpting the main subject with precise vectors.
  [4] Illumination: Adding highlights to represent the spark of consciousness.
